OL,3,CMedical group fined after sensitive
OL,4,Chealth data stolen in cyber attack
OL,6,FThe Medical Specialist Group LLP (MSG)
OL,7,Fhas been fined #100,000 after health
OL,8,Fdata was stolen in a cyber attack.
OL,10,FThe company, which Guernsey's
OL,11,Fgovernment contracts to provide
OL,12,Fspecialist care, had its server
OL,13,Fcompromised by criminals who accessed
OL,14,Femails which contained sensitive
OL,15,Fpatient details.
OL,17,FThe data regulator says the exact size
OL,18,Fof the breach is unknown, but
OL,19,Fthousands of emails were vulnerable.
