OL,4,Chealth data stolen in cyber attack
OL,6,FIt adds this theft of personal details
OL,7,Fled to multiple phishing campaigns
OL,8,F"over a series of months" - where
OL,9,Ffraudsters attempted to steal further
OL,10,Fsensitive information directly from
OL,11,Fpatients.
OL,13,FThe data breach happened in August
OL,14,F2021, but was only detected and
OL,15,Freported by The MSG three and a half
OL,16,Fmonths later after it received several
OL,17,Fsuspicious emails.
