OL,6,FAn inquiry by Guernsey's Data
OL,7,FProtection Authority found that The
OL,8,FMSG "failed to take reasonable steps
OL,9,Fto ensure the security of personal
OL,10,Fdata", routinely not installing
OL,11,Fsecurity updates over 13 months which
OL,12,Fit says directly led to the email
OL,13,Fserver being exploited and "other
OL,14,Fcritical vulnerabilities".
OL,16,FThe regulator also notes there "were
OL,17,Fseveral missed opportunities to detect
OL,18,Funauthorised access" due to flaws in
OL,19,Fthe company's use of threat detection
OL,20,Fsoftware.
