OL,6,FIt also identified issues with the
OL,7,FMSG's internal investigation,
OL,8,Fincluding that the company failed to
OL,9,Ffind the root cause of the server
OL,10,Fvulnerability.
OL,12,FGuernsey's Data Protection
OL,13,FCommissioner, Brent Homan, explains:
OL,14,F"Medical information demands the
OL,15,Fhighest level of safeguard protection
OL,16,Fagainst cyber attacks, and the
OL,17,Fsanction in this matter reflects that
OL,18,Fthe measures in place at MSG fell well
OL,19,Fshort of legal requirements.
