OL,4,Chealth data stolen in cyber attack
OL,6,F"Looking to the future, the new CEO
OL,7,Fhas committed to positioning MSG as a
OL,8,Fleader in the health sector for
OL,9,Fsafeguarding data.
OL,11,F"In fact, the action plan developed by
OL,12,FMSG not only meets, but exceeds what
OL,13,Fwe would have expected. I am confident
OL,14,Fthat when the plan has been fulfilled,
OL,15,FBailiwick residents, many of whom use
OL,16,FMSG's services, should benefit from an
OL,17,Fexceptional level of protection for
OL,18,Ftheir health information."
